Detailed Description

Reads data from an infile and shows it on the map and, in some cases, some data in the dialog.

Currently handles the following "records", unknown lines are skiped:

  • NODE: mapID.nodeID
  • TURNDESCRIPTION: mapID.fromNodeID;mapID.toNodeID; Old turndesc;Old crossingkind
